# Database Design
# Restaurant Management System

User:
   - id (Primary Key)
   - name (string)
   - email (email)
   - phone_number (char)

Category:
   - id (Primary Key)
   - name (string)

Food:
   - id(PK)
   - name (string)
   - description (text)
   - price (float)
   - category_id (Foreign Key)(one to many)

Table:
   - id(PK)
   - table_number (string)
   - capacity (int)
   - status (available/occupied) (boolean)

Order:
   - id(PK)
   - user_id(FK)(one- to -many)
   - quantity (int)
   - total_price (float)

OrderItem(Junction Table):
   - id (PK)
   - order_id(FK)
   - food_id(FK)